# CHANGELOG

## 0.1.3 - 2025/04/08
- Fixed prediction dates being one day short
- Move buttons to bottom of screen
- Add counter with days remaining/to go
- Stop predicted days appearing in the previous month on the calendar
- Fix issues with DST
- Fix issues with native import giving false errors

## 0.1.2 - 2025/02/09
- Added mood and flow markers
- Fixed daylight savings time bug
- Updated menu layout
- Hide menu on startup

## 0.1.1 - 2025/01/13
- Improved predictions
- Some formatting updates e.g. highlighting only today's date
- External formats for imports

## 0.1.0 - 2024/12/14
- Initial version
